{"name":"Ward Reading","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You ask your willing oracle ally to provide a quick word of divination to you.</p>\n<p>They use their reaction to grant you a +1 circumstance bonus to Reflex saves until the end of your next turn.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.magic-specializations-effects.B2aI3kNv0FNr0DO7]{Effect: Ward Reading}</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"ward-reading","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["hb_consult","linguistic"]},"actionType":{"value":"action"},"category":"interaction","actions":{"value":1},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneAction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686127058088,"modifiedTime":1686136440445,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"h716hPkiblkqwW33"}
{"name":"Mindwall","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You impose a block in your foe's mind. Choose an enemy within 30 feet and attempt an Occultism check against their Will DC.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> Choose an ally or yourself. They become @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Concealed]{Concealed} to the enemy until the end of your next turn. They can use this concealment to attempt to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.XMcnh4cSI32tljXa]{Hide} or @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Sneak]{Sneak}. The enemy becomes the target of your expertise. Any creature who previously was the target of your expertise loses that designation.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> Choose an ally or yourself. They become concealed to the enemy until the end of your next turn, but they can't use this concealment to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.XMcnh4cSI32tljXa]{Hide} or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.VMozDqMMuK5kpoX4]{Sneak}. The enemy becomes the target of your expertise. Any creature who previously was the target of your expertise loses that designation.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The enemy becomes the target of your expertise. Any creature who previously was the target of your expertise loses that designation.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The enemy's mind rebuffs your attempt. They are immune to your @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.magic-specializations-actions.ipPyn59iPQhWCHr6]{Mindwall} for 1 hour. If they were the target of your expertise, they lose that designation.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"mindwall","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["hb_expertise","psychic"]},"actionType":{"value":"action"},"category":"offensive","actions":{"value":1},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneAction.webp","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.83psRKW3xvt6mKjq"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"