{"name":"Outperform","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You challenge a creature to match your talents. Choose a creature within 30 feet and a skill. If the creature has an intelligence modifier lower than -3, this action has no effect. Attempt a Performance check against the creature's Will DC.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature must spend their first action on their next turn answering your challenge. When they do, they attempt a check using Performance or your chosen skill against your Performance DC. If they fail, they take a -2 circumstance penalty to checks using your chosen skill until the end of their next turn, and you can use @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.magic-specializations-actions.zED6EOsCG6Q1SkZk]{Outperform} against them as a free action at the start of your next turn. They become the target of your expertise. Any creature who previously was the target of your expertise loses that designation.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature must spend their first action on their next turn answering your challenge. When they do, they attempt a check using Performance or your chosen skill against your Performance DC. If they fail, they take a -2 circumstance penalty to checks using your chosen skill until the end of their next turn. They become the target of your expertise. Any creature who previously was the target of your expertise loses that designation.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.magic-specializations-effects.t0UW4KvJEbzouftu]{Effect: Outperform}</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The enemy becomes the target of your expertise. Any creature who previously was the target of your expertise loses that designation.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> You embarrass yourself. The creature is immune to your @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.magic-specializations-actions.zED6EOsCG6Q1SkZk]{Outperform} for 1 hour. If they were the target of your expertise, they lose that designation.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"outperform","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["bard","hb_expertise","mental"]},"actionType":{"value":"action"},"category":"offensive","actions":{"value":1},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneAction.webp","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.fMWdbT4eYO3yZQkx"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686127185576,"modifiedTime":1686135509202,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"zED6EOsCG6Q1SkZk"}
